==French==

===Etymology===
Stems from l'ore de = In the era of

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /lɔʁ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /lOR/

===Conjunction===
'''lors'''
# [[when]]
# At the time of

====Usage note====
It is normally followed with [[de]], i.e. [[lors de]]
